<p class="page" id="a2552092">[Page 92]</p>
<p>a bit of persuasion, I got them to go away quietly.</p>
<p>I reckon it would have served them quite right, if the boys had smashed their joint right in, for they really all bring it on themselves by this sort of thing.</p>
<p>They have a new way now for describing a drunken man when he is playing up, they call it "Showing", &amp; they say that so &amp; so is going to "show" well tonight.</p>
<p>Last night I was promised my 3rd stripe in a day or so which would make me a Sergeant, pretty rapid promotion if you like.</p>
<p>Bridge is all the go here now we play it every opportunity we get</p>
